              class="absolute top-2 right-2 z-20 w-6 h-6 bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs leading-none">✕</button>
          </label>
          <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mt-1">JPG, PNG, WebP — Maks 2MB</p>
